headline: LeadingResponse Appoints Surya Chikkala as Chief Digital & Technology Officer
summary: TAMPA, Fla., October 14, 2025--LeadingResponse, the national leader in consumer engagement, announces Surya Chikkala as its new Chief Digital & Technology Officer. In this role, Surya will lead LeadingResponse’s engineering and technical vision, company’s mission and its long-term growth strategy.
